BUILDING
--------
- update the Makefile and point INSTALL_DIR to your MySQL Cluster installation
- then do 'make'

RUNNING
-------
- You might have to export the LD_LIBRARY_PATH to INSTALL_DIR/lib
- ./ndb_record_size  (no args will print out help)

TESTED
------
- Compiles on Ubuntu..
- Compiles with 5.1.22
- gcc version 4.1.2 20060928 (prerelease) (Ubuntu 4.1.1-13ubuntu5)
